    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>\n                  A logistic formula in biology is applied to analyze deaths by COVID-19 for both of the first and the second waves in Japan. We then discuss ends of both waves and their mortality ratios. The meaning of population\n                  <jats:italic>N</jats:italic>\n                  in an epidemic is discussed.\n                </jats:p>",
